thread.title: Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text: The online booking process was easy and the price was very competitive and excellent value for money. Yes the hire car company was off airport, but the shuttle was process was quick and efficient. There were no surprises and what we paid on booking was all we paid, no other costs. Have recommended Airport Rentals to friends and they have already booked and also found them very competitive.
